{
  "page": "Hallis Hornwood",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">Not to be confused with <a href=\"/index.php/Halys_Hornwood\" title=\"Halys Hornwood\">Halys Hornwood</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hornwood\" title=\"House Hornwood\"><img alt=\"House Hornwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/03/House_Hornwood.svg/50px-House_Hornwood.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/03/House_Hornwood.svg/75px-House_Hornwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/03/House_Hornwood.svg/100px-House_Hornwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Hallis Hornwood<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Mad Hal</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hornwood\" title=\"House Hornwood\"><img alt=\"House Hornwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/03/House_Hornwood.svg/50px-House_Hornwood.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/03/House_Hornwood.svg/75px-House_Hornwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/03/House_Hornwood.svg/100px-House_Hornwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nMad Hal</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hornwood\" title=\"House Hornwood\">House Hornwood</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">Blacks</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Wolf_Pack\" title=\"Wolf Pack\">Wolf Pack</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">Northmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Hallis Hornwood</b>, known as <b>Mad Hal</b>, was a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hornwood\" title=\"House Hornwood\">House Hornwood</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hallis_Hornwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Hallis accompanied Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Cregan_Stark\" title=\"Cregan Stark\">Cregan Stark</a> south to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>. After war's end, Hal and <a href=\"/index.php/Timotty_Snow\" title=\"Timotty Snow\">Timotty Snow</a> founded the <a href=\"/index.php/Wolf_Pack\" title=\"Wolf Pack\">Wolf Pack</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Free_company\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Free company\">free company</a> which sailed from <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a> for the <a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hallis_Hornwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Under the Regents - The Hooded Hand.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403151838\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.061 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.249 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 441/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10433/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6230/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 526/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 660/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.73 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  239.417      1 -total\n 85.51%  204.725      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 84.65%  202.662      1 Template:Infobox\n 12.09%   28